documentation.text:
@dev Grants `DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE`, `MINTER_ROLE`, and `PAUSER_ROLE` to the account that
 deploys the contract.
 Ranks
   1-> Common
   2-> Rare
   3-> Epic? Legendary
   4-> Divine

@dev Creates `amount` new tokens for `to`, of token type `id`.
 See {ERC1155-_mint}.
 Requirements:
 - the caller must have the `MINTER_ROLE`.

typeDescriptions.typeString: function (uint256) pure returns (struct Voido.ItemProperty memory[] memory)
